# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

The Reliability Roll-up report summarizes the reliability performance of selected Nobl9 SLOs over a calendar or rolling time frame. Reports can use filters to build an automatic hierarchy or a custom JSON hierarchy to group SLOs into folders.

The report scope must be defined with either `filters` or `custom_hierarchy`. These fields are mutually exclusive, but one of them is required.

Custom hierarchy can contain up to 8 nodes at each hierarchy level.

