## Custom Hierarchy JSON Shape

The `custom_hierarchy` field accepts a JSON-encoded list of folders. Each folder supports:

- `displayName` - folder display name.
- `children` - optional list of child folders with the same shape.
- `slos` - optional list of SLO references. Each SLO reference supports `name`, `project`, and optional `displayName`.

